data.description: Desire the charm & location of what Grandview Heights gives you, but may be need a first floor master, full basement, first floor laundry and large walk-in primary suite shower? Well look no further as we have the home for you! Pride of home ownership will be extremely apparent upon entering as this has been a family home for over 30+ years! In 2020, a 1000sqft addition was added and has an open concept into the kitchen which is great for entertaining your neighbors! Enjoy your morning coffee on either porch - you have one in both the front and back! The backyard is fenced in and contains a 3-car garage, one of the few in the area! You do not want to miss this one!
